nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.38

Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.38 is the thirty-eighth issue of the 6th volume of the Star Wars Comic UK published on September 20, 2012. It includes a free gift, a Disc Shooter and features Top 5 Creatures, an Episode guide to The Box, and Bounty Hunter Smackdown, a hypothetical match between Cad Bane and Aurra Sing.
The comic included the comic strip Sabotage.
